name: James Robinson
description:
I am a very active and attractive guy who enjoys being on the go. I love to keep moving. I eat healthy food and go to the gym every day. I believe that work hard pays off. I am a very hardworking and determined person who believes in true love. I think that both parties have to work hard in order for a relationship to be successful….
I am looking for a person who also enjoys life and also very active like me. I see my baby (my man) like a man with a sense of humor. With stable life position and of course with great family values. He is my superman who is goal-oriented and self-confident. Well, of course he is my hero! I want to fall in love head over heels and to make my beloved the happiest person in the world.
